    • ClientConsole

      public ClientConsole(String host, int port)
      ClientConsole is the Second layer of client. client console works with the ClientInterfaceController and with ChatClient.
      Parameters:
      host - - saves the ip-address string adress that allows client to connect to sever.
      port - - saves the port integer that allows client to connect to server.

    • accept

      public void accept(Object msg)
      Parameters:
      msg - Function operates as second layer. the function sends object(msg) to the @ChatClient when client wants to send a message to the server. the message advanced to the next layer until it sends to the server. We are here. Client UI -> Client UI Controller -> Client Console -> ChatClient -> EchoServer
